{"tid":1846622,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"各間醫院已經book左附近酒店 予醫護人員住宿","createTime":"2020-01-27T16:33:28.000Z","updateTime":"2020-01-27T16:51:40.000Z","uid":92347,"like":4,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"42f8a5126101dbb78ee9f37bf309ef084de3f6ef","tid":1846622,"uid":92347,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-27T16:33:28.000Z","msg":"以下係其中之一<br />\n<br />\n緊急！求fc!!! 荃灣嘅酒店租左百幾間房比武漢人？<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1846596\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1846596</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">留意如果酒店其中幾層封左，即係留左俾醫護人員<br />\n<br />\n每間醫院會book幾間唔同既酒店，大家唔好住近醫院既酒店！<br />\n<br />\n以上消息來自幫醫院訂酒店既一手資料，訂酒店係各醫院自已決定，未有一個list包含所有酒店 </span></strong>"},{"pid":"0a91463ca2330b9d5de5aa334998e8f947050b34","tid":1846622,"uid":92347,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-27T16:36:55.000Z","msg":"幫俾其他人睇"},{"pid":"f93cf144f565414fce8f0a78559ff94ea393f333","tid":1846622,"uid":237227,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-27T16:40:37.000Z","msg":"推推，合理過無端端大量武漢人"},{"pid":"8a649150e08b405cd90e0bdf8db5bf846b1b74cf","tid":1846622,"uid":92347,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"f93cf144f565414fce8f0a78559ff94ea393f333","tid":1846622,"uid":237227,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-27T16:40:37.000Z","msg":"推推，合理過無端端大量武漢人"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-27T16:41:21.000Z","msg":"武漢人唔知，但酒店係一定會for醫護，前1/2日訂左"},{"pid":"5d08b04a654d98b24105e182a8e8e0a32831f511","tid":1846622,"uid":117235,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-27T16:44:05.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/0OX34y3.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F0OX34y3.jpg&h=d930b64f&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/2WNPfFJ.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F2WNPfFJ.jpg&h=033f6cbd&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"ece6de9ee6d603406d8